item.itemName: HOLD Management for PhDs Summer program

1. Management for PhDs Summer program - We partner with The Graduate School on an executive education program for PhDs from across the University. Traditionally we have been in the Hub for 8 Tuesdays in the summer. This year that would be June 17, 24, July 1,8,25,22,29, August 5. We would need a 50 person classroom from 8am-6pm. (reserving L110 for this)
